summary: What do you think the chances are that Phil will give an update about the gc, liveshows, or the hiatus in general in his new...
question: What do you think the chances are that Phil will give an update about the gc, liveshows, or the hiatus in general in his new video tomorrow?!
answer: I don’t think he’s going to say anything at all about Dan. He may mention the gaming channel, because that’s half his business to talk about, and he may mention his own liveshows or whatever, but as far as “when will dan be back” type questions, not a chance.
